title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Grimm/Zim/Leber/Ron&Hobie
description: Bruce Boudreau opens the show, followed by Gophers vox Mike Grimm and Mike Zimmer to finish the hour. Ben Leber in studio midway through, then Ron Johnson & Hobie Artigue are in studio the final hour!
